                        "While many commenters critiqued certain aspects of the proposed form and format of the short form and long form disclosures, the Bureau received no specific comments regarding the proposed general tabular format requirement for those disclosures. See the section-by-section analysis of \u00a7\u20091005.18(b)(7)(i) below for discussion of comments regarding grouping and other format requirements."
